          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/16/35428890/241eba6e4c00020975cf91170050f435_7966041363779991033.png",
                "id": "talent52977",
                "key": "Line Bayonet Thrust EX",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Line Bayonet Thrust EX"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro DMG</span>.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">After the Skill finalizes:</span> If your Hand has <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Overcharged Ball</span>: <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Discard</span> 1 of them and heal the character on your team that has taken the most damage for 1 HP.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/16/35428890/7ddd81e7004a3f8abc09fb6b867ab7c4_7674753437641307010.png",
                "id": "talent79479",
                "key": "Short-Range Rapid Interdiction Fire ",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Short-Range Rapid Interdiction Fire "
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro DMG</span>, creates 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Secondary Explosive Shells</span> on the opponent's side of the field.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Secondary Explosive Shells</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Combat Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">After a character switch takes place on this side of the field:</span> Deal 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro DMG</span> to the character switched to.<br><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Usage(s): 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/16/35428890/1af428c7d17f9063ae85fc6340f6d630_1459027249928456837.png",
                "id": "talent23198",
                "key": "Ring of Bursting Grenades ",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Ring of Bursting Grenades "
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Passive Skill</span></p><p>(Passive) <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">After an opponent's character takes Overloaded reaction DMG:</span> Create 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Overcharged Ball</span> card in your Hand (Once per Round)</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Overcharged Ball</span></strong><br><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Combat Action</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Combat Action</span>: Deal 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro DMG</span> to the opponent's active character.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When this card is Discarded:</span> Deal 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro DMG</span> to the opponent's active character.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/16/35428890/131727ae6d876016cdaa5731e5e05974_3811165458321147585.png",
                "id": "talent99609",
                "key": "Vertical Force Coordination",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Vertical Force Coordination"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Event Card</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Combat Action</span>: Deal 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro DMG</span> to the opponent's active character.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When this card is Discarded:</span> Deal 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro DMG</span> to the opponent's active character.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/18/35428890/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_3402339906551992576.png",
                "id": "talent77059",
                "key": "Overcharged Ball",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/18/35428890/5dca55a012526872199ffb25f0129241_3413339039687227629.png",
                "title": "Overcharged Ball"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Pyro and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Melt</span>: DMG +2 for this instance</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Vaporize</span>: DMG +2 for this instance</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Overloaded</span>: DMG +2 for this instance, the target is forcibly switched to the next character</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning Flame</span>] that will deal 1 Pyro DMG at the end of the Round (Takes effect once, max 2 stacks)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/16/35428890/d714b3b669cc08d1d8e34464fd7a3630_8145543588671898342.png",
                "id": "talent56874",
                "key": "Pyro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Pyro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Physical DMG</span></strong><br>Physical DMG will not apply any Elements, nor can it engage in Elemental Reactions.<br></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Combat Action</span></strong><br>After you finish 1 Combat Action, it will be your opponent's turn.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Playing a card from your Hand with this rule is also a Combat Action rather than a Fast Action</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Discard</span></strong><br>Use Action Cards or Character Skill effects to Discard Action Cards from Hand or Deck.<br></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Usage(s)</span></strong><br>After this card's effect is triggered, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage</span> of it will be consumed.<br>This card will be discarded immediately once it has 0 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usages</span> remaining.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/16/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_3440830012552666929.png",
                "id": "talent55221",
                "key": "Detailed Rules",
